---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TransformCTA from '../../components/TransformCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Botox Lip Flip (giro de labio) - Renasci Medical Spa"
  description="Técnica sutil que realza el labio superior, creando definición y efecto de volumen natural sin rellenos. Agenda tu cita en Renasci Medical Spa."
>
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-32 bg-black text-white text-center">
    <div class="px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-0 md:mt-4">
      <div class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/30 to-pink-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6 border border-white/30">Neurotoxin & Dermal Filler Injections</div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-4">Botox Lip Flip</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">Define el labio superior con un efecto de “volteo” sutil y natural sin usar rellenos.</p>
      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6 inline-block border border-white/20">
        <div class="text-sm text-white/80 mb-1">Precio desde</div>
        <div class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">$75</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-white/80 mt-1">Duración: 15 min</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="#detalles" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-90 hover:-translate-y-[2px] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-white/50">Ver Detalles<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path></svg></a>
        <a href="tel:+13855550123" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-[#10B981] text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-90 hover:-translate-y-[2px] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-call/50" aria-label="Llamar Renasci"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>(385) 555-0123</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <nav class="bg-background py-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Inicio</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
        <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Servicios</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
        <li class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Botox Lip Flip</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="h-[2px] w-full bg-primary"></div>

  <section id="detalles" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-stretch">
        <div class="relative group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden h-full min-h-[420px] lg:min-h-[520px]">
          <img src="/img/services/Botox-Lip-Flip.jpg" alt="Botox Lip Flip" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="min-h-[420px] lg:min-h-[520px] flex">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-purple-50 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 h-full flex-1">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6">Botox Lip Flip</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p class="mb-4">El <strong>Botox Lip Flip</strong> utiliza pequeñas dosis de neurotoxina para relajar suavemente el músculo del labio superior, logrando un efecto de volteo que crea definición y apariencia de mayor volumen sin rellenos.</p>
              <p class="mb-4">Es ideal para quienes buscan un resultado sutil y natural. La técnica realza el contorno del labio superior, manteniendo tu expresividad y proporciones faciales.</p>
              <p>El procedimiento es rápido, seguro y con resultados visibles en pocos días, manteniéndose de forma óptima entre 3–4 meses.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white text-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div>
          <span class="mx-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 21a9 9 0 1 0 0-18 9 9 0 0 0 0 18z" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div><span class="mx-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg></span><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div></div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-[#F3A2A7] mb-4">Beneficios del Tratamiento</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Ventajas clave del Botox Lip Flip</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-transparent text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] hover:bg-[#F3A2A7]/15"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#F3A2A7]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Define el Labio Superior</h3><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Aporta contorno y realce sutil sin añadir volumen externo.</p></div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border-2 border-primary bg-transparent text-white hover:ring-2 hover:ring-primary/60"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 border-2 border-primary hover:bg-primary/15"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Aspecto Natural</h3><p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Mantiene expresividad y proporciones sin apariencia de relleno.</p></div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border-2 border-primary bg-transparent text-white hover:ring-2 hover:ring-primary/60"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 border-2 border-primary hover:bg-primary/15"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Rápido y Seguro</h3><p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Procedimiento de pocos minutos y resultados visibles en días.</p></div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border-2 border-primary bg-transparent text-white hover:ring-2 hover:ring-primary/60"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 border-2 border-primary hover:bg-primary/15"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Sin Rellenos</h3><p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Realce mediante relajación muscular, sin material de relleno.</p></div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border-2 border-primary bg-transparent text-white hover:ring-2 hover:ring-primary/60"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 border-2 border-primary hover:bg-primary/15"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Resultados Consistentes</h3><p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Duración típica 3–4 meses con mantenimiento periódico.</p></div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border-2 border-primary bg-transparent text-white hover:ring-2 hover:ring-primary/60"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 border-2 border-primary hover:bg-primary/15"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Mejora la Simetría</h3><p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Ayuda a armonizar el contorno entre ambos lados del labio.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-primary"></div><span class="mx-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 21a9 9 0 1 0 0-18 9 9 0 0 0 0 18z" /></svg></span><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-primary"></div></div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">Proceso del Tratamiento</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Rápido, cómodo y con resultados naturales</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-primary via-pink-400 to-purple-500 rounded-full opacity-30 hidden lg:block"></div>
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-pink-500/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/20"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">1</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Evaluación Inicial</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Análisis del contorno natural del labio y definición del plan.</p></div></div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><img src="/img/services/first.jpg" alt="Evaluación inicial" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-pink-500/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-500/20"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">2</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Preparación del Área</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Limpieza, desinfección y marcado preciso de puntos.</p></div></div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><img src="/img/services/second.jpg" alt="Preparación" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/10 to-teal-500/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-emerald-500/20"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">3</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Aplicación Precisa</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Microinyecciones estratégicas en el músculo del labio superior.</p></div></div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><img src="/img/services/third.jpg" alt="Aplicación precisa" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-500/10 to-pink-500/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-rose-500/20"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">4</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Cuidados y Seguimiento</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Recomendaciones post-tratamiento y evaluación de resultados en días.</p></div></div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><img src="/img/services/fourth.jpg" alt="Seguimiento" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white text-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div>
          <span class="mx-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-[#F3A2A7] mb-4">Preguntas Frecuentes</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Resolvemos dudas comunes sobre Botox Lip Flip</p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-transparent text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center"><div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] hover:bg-[#F3A2A7]/15"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#F3A2A7]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg></div>¿En qué se diferencia del relleno de labios?</h3><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed pl-11">Relaja el músculo para definir el labio; los rellenos agregan volumen.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-transparent text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center"><div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] hover:bg-[#F3A2A7]/15"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#F3A2A7]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg></div>¿Cuánto tiempo dura el efecto?</h3><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed pl-11">Usualmente 3–4 meses; se puede repetir para mantener el resultado.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-transparent text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center"><div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] hover:bg-[#F3A2A7]/15"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#F3A2A7]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path></svg></div>¿Afecta la funcionalidad del labio?</h3><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed pl-11">No; técnica precisa que mantiene funcionalidad normal.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-primary"></div><span class="mx-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" /></svg></span><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-primary"></div></div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">Lo Que Dicen Nuestros Pacientes</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Experiencias reales con resultados sutiles y naturales</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
